## Summary

This project contains educational content written by **Santiago Correa Vergara**, based on personal experience and extended research during cybersecurity training. While the structure loosely follows publicly available government bootcamp formats, the explanations, insights, and additional content are original and do **not** reproduce copyrighted material.

